OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSpain tobacco firms to pay 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto clear cigarette butts   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tobacco companies will now be charged  
OL,6, to clean up cigarette butts off the    
OL,7, streets and beaches of Spain, according
OL,8, to new environmental regulations.      
OL,10,FMillions of butts are thrown away each 
OL,11,Fyear - releasing toxic plastic waste   
OL,12,Fwhich can take decades to break down.  
OL,14,FFigures from 2020 show around a fifth  
OL,15,Fof adult Spaniards smoke everyday.     
OL,17,FThe rules came into force on Friday,   
OL,18,Fbut it remains unclear how they will be
OL,19,Fimplemented and whether costs are      
OL,20,Flikely to be passed on to consumers.   
